FOXE BASIN.
CANADA.
DNC 28.
24 FOOT CANOE, GREEN HULL, THREE PERSONS ON BOARD,
OVERDUE IGLOOLIK (69-23N 081-48W) TO
HALL BEACH (68-47N 081-13W). VESSELS IN VICINITY
REQUESTED TO KEEP A SHARP LOOKOUT, ASSIST IF
POSSIBLE. REPORT ANY SIGHTINGS OR INFORMATION TO
THE NEAREST MARINE COMMUNICATIONS AND TRAFFIC
SERVICES CENTRE.
